The goal of the LCES framework is to transform the "precariat"—the new dangerous class of workers made vulnerable by AI dependency—into a procedurally literate workforce that can leverage synthetic intelligence without losing its critical reasoning or moral authority. As we redefine the "reasonable person" for the AI era, the standard will increasingly rest on one’s ability to conduct the LCES sequence: to Blueprint with precision, Research with skepticism, Construct with clarity, Challenge with rigor, and Decide with integrity.   

